title: My Premium hextech chest was not given to me
body: Me and my friend started a League Of Legends accounts together once we hit level 5 we check to see if we had our premiums chest butt i did not receive one and my friend got two

replies.body:
Hey there,

That's odd, are you sure it's not there? Perhaps you just missed it.

If you're sure you haven't received it you'll need to [submit a ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/requests/new) to Player Support as they're the only ones who can help with issues relating to your account.
